title: Hey Tumblr,
body:
I’m just saying, tumblr asked for RDJ to have a baby girl…and he had a baby girl. Tumblr asked for Brie Larson to be Captain Marvel…. and now she’s Captain Marvel.

So.. since Tumblr is obviously full of witches..

How about we work on getting Chris Evans in a live action Disney Hercules movie? Think about how great it would be. You know you want it, let’s make it happen!

Fic: Hollow Spirits

Hollow Spirits - on AO3

616 Carol/Jess, rated T, 6500 words.

Carol is missing something. She is supposed to have her memory back, yet there is an emptiness inside her. No one will listen and nothing can help. Except Tony Stark and a bottle of Jack.

My late contribution to the 2018 Carol/Jess mini bang. Thanks to @einheriar for beta.

body:
Marvel rant #27

I think it’s funny that the Captain Marvel trailer came out and made us feel all good inside. We became pumped with girl power and hope for a good resolution of Avengers 4 without too much heartbreak

But then like literally not a month later Chris Evans is like yo finished filming avengers 4 #peaceout Had a great time, what a blessing this was for 8 yrs. Then all of a sudden we are reminded of the despair and horror that’s still to come and what it means for his character and that’s not okay soo…like marvel… y'all need to chill

And I’ll miss him
